{
  "stem": "24130.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I says-- you know, to the mother-- my aunt said, to the mother, how could you let your son be such a bad boy?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She says, ah, he's a child.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He wasn't child.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was about 20, 21 years old.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He wasn't child anymore.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We didn't have much to do with the priest, really.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He-- we always knew that he's an anti-Semite.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because he used to preach-- they used to tell us, some peasants used to tell us that he used to preach in church against the Jews, specially before Christmas.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So before Christmas, the-- some-- Jew-- some non-Jews, the Jews used to be afraid of the-- of the-- at Christmastime, of the peasants.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So you wouldn't-- what would happen on Christmas?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I don't think anything happened.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they used to say, that the priest had a sermon.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he said that we killed their God, and they should not bother with us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they should, you know?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Some of them were nice-- they told us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the Jews stayed away from the priest.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we had other people that we were very close, like the-- in the-- in the-- the principal from school.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was very close with my father.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he used to tell us things.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because he used to go to church.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he used to say that he discussions with the priest, that he shouldn't make the-- the-- the non-Jewish people so anti-Semite against the Jews.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But he says, he couldn't convince him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The principal used to say, I can't convince him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
